Class MultipleInvocationListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.jsonrpc4j.MultipleInvocationListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InvocationListener

    public class MultipleInvocationListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements InvocationListener
    InvocationListener that supports the use of multiple InvocationListeners called one after another.
